title: McCarthy Blocks Democrats Schiff, Swalwell From House Intelligence Panel

description: Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez (D-NY) is gunning to be the vice ranking member on House Oversight Committee, which would presumably place her second in line to become the ranking member or chairwoman if Democrats retake the House in 2024.
